quran[93]{c,v,t}:
  27,1,"Ăs. Atnan issekniyen n LeqwĂŽan, akked Tezmamt ipbegginen."
  27,2,"D nnhaya u d abecceĂŽ i lmumnin:"
  27,3,"wid ibedden i tĂ©allit, ippaken zzakat, ipputebbten $ef laxeĂŽt nnsen."
  27,4,"Ih, wid ur numin ara s laxeĂŽt, NcebbeĂȘ asen igiten nnsen, d$a ddebdeben."
  27,5,"Widak, fellasen aĂąaqeb ucmit mavi. Di laxeĂŽt, d nitni ara ixesĂŽen ugwar."
  27,6,"S tidep, keĂ§Ă§ iusa k id LeqwĂŽan, s$uĂŽ Bab n Ă»Ă»wab, Amusnaw."
  27,7,"Mi inna Musa i twacult is: ""nek wala$ times, ad awen d awi$, segs, asali, ne$ ad awen d awi$ asafu iĂŽeqqen, amar a ppesseĂȘmum""."
  27,8,"Mi ibbwev $uĂŽes, ipwanced: ""ad iĂŽqu wayen illan di tmes, akked wayen i as d izzin. Gedha s Ăebbi, Mass imavalen!"
  27,9,"A Musa! Ih, Nek d Ăebbi, Uzmir, Bab n Ă»Ă»wab."
  27,10,"VeggeĂŽ taĂąkwazt ik""! Mi p iwala la tesseĂȘĂŽiĂźiw, amzun d azrem, ibren, ur iwexxeĂŽ. ""A Musa! Ur ppagwad! Ar $uĂŽI, ih, ur ppagwaden imazanen,"
  27,11,"siwa win idensen, sinna, iu$al iwqem, deffir tuccva. Nek, s tidep, PsemmiĂȘe$, PĂȘunnu$."
  27,12,"Ger afus ik di loib ik, a d iffe$ d amellal, ur ihlik. Si tza issekniyen, i FerĂąun akked ugdud is. Nitni, war ccekk, d agdud icemten""."
  27,13,"Mi ten id usan issekniyen nneÂŁ, Ăąinani, nnan: ""wagi iban d ssĂȘur""."
  27,14,"Ugin ten s ddens d pnefxa, u, deg iman nnsen, pputebbten. Wali, ihi, amek tevĂŽa d ifessaden."
  27,15,"Ni$ Nefka tamusni i Dawed akked Sliman. Nnan: ""ccekĂŽan i Ăebbi, i a$ Ismenyafen i waĂźaĂ» n yimdanen iumnen""."
  27,16,"Sliman iwĂŽet Dawed, u inna: ""a yimdanen! Nepwaselmed tutlayt n yifĂŽax; ippunefk a$ si yal cci. Ayagi, s tidep, ard lfevl n Ă»Ă»eĂȘ""."
  27,17,"Pwajemmlen d, i Sliman, iÂČĂąsekĂŽiwen is si leonun, imdanen, ifĂŽax. Mdarraren."
  27,18,"Armi, mi bbwven ar te$zut n twevfin, tenna d tweĂźuft: ""a yaweĂźĂźuf, kecmemt ar ixxamen nnkwent, mulac, war ccekk, a kwent iĂ©d Sliman, neppa akked iĂąsekĂŽiwen is, ur faqen""."
  27,19,"IcmumeĂȘ, ivĂ»a, $ef wayen d tenna. Inna: ""a Mass iw! Err iyi ad snemmre$ l$it iK, is i $ T$atev, nek akked imawlan iw; ad xedme$ ise$ ara TĂŽaviv; Ssekcem iyi, s uĂȘunu K, ar imdanen iK imaĂąnen""."
  27,20,"Issefqed ifĂŽax, inna: ""acimi ur wala$ ara iĂ§Ă§ibib, day d l$ayeb?"
  27,21,"War ccekk, ad sĂąaddi$ fellas aĂąaqeb uqsiĂȘ, ne$ a t zlu$, ne$ a d iawi tasebbiwt tubrizt""."
  27,22,"Ur iĂąaĂźĂźel ara. Inna d: ""fehme$ ayen ur tefhimev. Usi$ d $uĂŽek si Saba, s usali unĂ»iĂȘ."
  27,23,"Ih, ufi$ en tameĂźĂźut d tagelliĂź nnsen. Ippunefk as si yal cci. ÂŁuĂŽes asgeld abarar."
  27,24,"Ufi$ p in, neppat akked ugdud is, la kennun i yiĂźij, war Ăebbi. CciĂźan icebbeĂȘ asen igiten nnsen. IveĂŽf iten seg ubrid, d$a nitni ur pwanhan."
  27,25,"Acimi ur knan ara i Ăebbi, id Issufu$en lesrar, di tmurt akked igenwan, i IĂ©ĂŽan ayen teppeffrem u ayen d tepberriĂȘem?"
  27,26,"Ăebbi, ur illi ĂŽebbi siwa Neppa, Mass n usgeld ameqwĂŽaĂȘan""."
  27,27,"Inna: ""a nĂ©eĂŽ ma tessawlev d tidep, ne$ ma keĂ§Ă§ seg ikeddaben."
  27,28,"ĂuĂȘ s tebĂŽap iw agi, veggeĂŽ asen p, sinna, wexxeĂŽ asen, wali acu ara d rren""."
  27,29,"Tenna: ""a yimvebbĂŽen, tepwaveggeĂŽ iyi d tebĂŽap tukyist."
  27,30,"Ih, s$uĂŽ Sliman. Apan: s yisem n Ăebbi AĂȘnin IpĂȘunun."
  27,31,"Ur ssem$waĂŽet ara iman nnwen $uĂŽi, aset ed $uĂŽi, d imvuĂąen""."
  27,32,"Tenna: ""a yimvebbĂŽen, fket ed ĂŽĂŽay nnwen af lameĂŽ iw. Ur pseyyi$ lameĂŽ, siwa garawen""."
  27,33,"Nnan: ""nekwni d imawlan n tezmert, nesĂąa lemĂȘella tuqsiĂȘt. LameĂŽ i kem. Muqel d acu ara d tseyyiv""."
  27,34,"Tenna: ""s tidep, igeldan ssefsaden tamdint ara kecmen. Sdullun imdanen is lĂąali. Akka ay xeddmen."
  27,35,"Nek, ad asen azne$ tarzeft, ad aĂŽou$ acu ara d awin imcegĂąan""."
  27,36,"Mi tebbwev ar Sliman, inna: ""day ad iyi tĂąawnem s terkunt? Ayen i yi Ifka Ăebbi, yif ayen i wen Ifka. D kunwi kan i ifeĂŽĂȘen, s terzeft nnwen."
  27,37,"U$al $uĂŽsen. Ih, a nĂŽuĂȘ $uĂŽsen s lĂąaskeĂŽ, iwumi ur zmiren. A ten id nessuffe$, syenna, ndellen, d imejĂźuĂȘen""."
  27,38,"Inna: ""a yimvebbĂŽen, anwa degwen, ara yi d iawin asgeld is, uqbel a yi d asen d imvuĂąen""?"
  27,39,"AĂąfrit si leonun, inna d: ""ad ak t id awi$, uqbel ma tekkrev seg umekkan ik. I wayagi, war ccekk, nek d uzmir muman""."
  27,40,"Inna d bab n tmusni si Tezmamt: ""nek ad ak t id awi$, uqbel a pfukkev asmeĂŽmec"". Mi t iwala irs ed $uĂŽes, inna: ""wagi si lfevl n Mass iw, ad iyi ijeĂŽĂŽeb ma ad snemmre$, ne$ ma ad jehle$. Win isnemmren, isnemmer kan i iman is. Win ijehl, ihi, Mass iw d AsĂąay, d Ukyis""."
  27,41,"Inna: ""bedlet as udem usgeld is, a nĂ©eĂŽ ma tepwanha, ne$ haap seg wid ur nepwanha""."
  27,42,"Mi d tusa, nnan as: ""day am wagi, usgeld inem""? Terra d: ""amzun d neppa"". ""Tusa ya$ d tmusni, uqbel neppat, nuzen."
  27,43,"IsĂŽuĂȘ ip wayen tunez, war Ăebbi. Tella, s tidep, seg ugdud ijehliyen""."
  27,44,"Nnan as: ""ekcem ar lbeĂŽo""! Mi t twala, t$il degs aman; tesban ed ifadden is. Inna: ""s tidep, d lbeĂŽo ulelluc imzin"". Tenna: ""a Mass iw! Ih, dense$ iman iw. Akked Sliman, unze$ aS i Ăebbi, Mass imavalen""."
  27,45,"Ni$ Nuzen ed, i Tamud, gmat sen ĂaliĂȘ: ""Ăąabdet Ăebbi""! Maca, rran snat n trebbuya$, ppemnamarent."
  27,46,"Inna: ""a yagdud iw! Acimi tep$awalem ar tucmip, uqbel ise$? Lemmer a ppeste$fĂŽem Ăebbi, ahat aĂȘunu fellawen""."
  27,47,"Nnan: ""tkeĂȘĂȘesev a$, keĂ§Ă§ akked wi iddan yidek"". Inna: ""lfal nnwen ar Ăebbi, u kunwi d agdud ara ippuhewwlen""."
  27,48,"Llan, di temdint, tza iterrasen i issefsaden di tmurt, ur pleqqimen."
  27,49,"Nnan: ""yyaw a nemmesgal s Ăebbi, ard a neĂ©vem deg iv fellas, neppa akked twacult is. Sinna, a nini i bab is: ur nelli d inagan n tmen$iwt n tawacult is. Ih, nekwni, d imawlan n tidep""."
  27,50,"Undin ticeĂŽkep, Nundi ticeĂŽkep, nitni ur faqen."
  27,51,"Wali amek tevĂŽa di tceĂŽkep nnsen. Nen$ed iten, nitni, akked ugdud nnsen, meĂŽĂŽa."
  27,52,"Atnan hudden ixxamen nnsen, ilmend n ddens nnsen. Deg wayagi, war ccekk, assekni i ugdud issnen."
  27,53,"Nsellek wid iumnen u llan pĂȘezziben."
  27,54,"I LuĂź, mi inna i ugdud is: ""teppeddum ar wayen n dir, u kunwi tepwalim."
  27,55,"Ih, kunwi teppeddum ar irgazen, teb$am ten, war tilawin. Ih, kunwi d agdud ur nessin""."
  27,56,"Tiririt n ugdud is, siwa mi d nnan: ""ssuff$et tawacult n LuĂź, si temdint nnwen, nitni d imdanen i ib$an tezdeg""."
  27,57,"Nsellek it, neppa akked twacult is, siwa tameĂźĂźut is. Nseyya a ppili seg wid igwran."
  27,58,"Nesse$li d fellasen ageffur. I icmet ugeffur n wid ippunedĂŽen!"
  27,59,"Ini: ""ccekĂŽan i Ăebbi. Talwit i imdanen iS, wid Ifren"". Ppif Ăebbi, ne$ ayen pcaraken?"
  27,60,"Day Win Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan, i wen d Isse$lin aman, seg igenni - Nessenkar, yissen, iqwiĂŽen ippembehwaoen, ur teĂȘwaoem a d tessem$im ttjuĂŽ is -, day illa ĂŽebbi, ar tama n Ăebbi? Maca, nitni d agdud issaĂądalen."
  27,61,"Day Win Irran tamurt d tanezdu$t, Irra degs isaffen, Irra yas idurar, Irra agadir ger sin ilellen, day illa ĂŽebbi ar tama n Ăebbi? XaĂźi, tegwti degsen, ur ssinen."
  27,62,"Day Win IssemĂȘasen i umevĂŽuĂŽ, mara S d isiwel; Itekksen ayen n dir; i kwen Ipparan d igensas di tmurt; day illa ĂŽebbi, ar tama n Ăebbi? Drus id tesmektayem."
  27,63,"Day Win i kwen Inehhun, di tillas n lberr akked yill, id Ippaznen avu, d abecceĂŽ n ccira uĂȘunu S; day illa ĂŽebbi, ar tama n Ăebbi? Ay AĂąlay Ăebbi, sennig wayen pcaraken!"
  27,64,"Day Win Ibeddun lxelq, sinna, Ippales as; ikwen I$aten seg igenni akked tmurt; day illa ĂŽebbi ar tama n Ăebbi? Ini: ""awit ed atebbet nnwen, ma tessawalem tidep""!"
  27,65,"Ini: ""tabavnit, di tmurt akked igenwan, ur p issin yiwen siwa Ăebbi. Ur Ă©ĂŽin melmi ara d kkren""."
  27,66,"Ih, tamusni nnsen ur tessawev ar laxeĂŽt? XaĂźi, nitni di ccekk fellas. XaĂźi, nitni, fellas, dre$len."
  27,67,"Nnan wid ijehlen: ""day ma nu$al d akal, am imezwura nne$, s tidep, fella$ tanekra?"
  27,68,"Ni$ waĂąĂąden a$ aya, i nekwni akw i imezwura nne$, zik. Ayagi, d timucuha kan imenza""."
  27,69,"Ini: ""iniget di tmurt, walit amek tevĂŽa d ibe$wviyen""."
  27,70,"Ur $webben fellasen, ur pxiqqi ilmend n nncub nnsen."
  27,71,"Nnan: ""melmi lemĂąahda agi, ma d tidep ay tessawalem""?"
  27,72,"Ini: ""kra n wayen i$ef tĂȘarem, ahat atan ivfeĂŽ kwen id""."
  27,73,"Mass ik, s tidep, meqqweĂŽ lfevl iS, $ef imdanen. Maca, tegwti degsen ur snemmiren."
  27,74,"Mass ik, s tidep, IĂ©ĂŽa ayen teffren idmaren nnsen, akked wayen d qqaĂŽen."
  27,75,"Ur illi wayen iffren, deg igenni akked tmurt, ur nuri di Tezmamt ipbegginen."
  27,76,"Ih, LeqwĂŽan agi iĂȘekku d i At IsĂŽail, tegwti n wayen i$ef mgarraden."
  27,77,"Neppa, war ccekk, ard nnhaya akked uĂȘunu i lmumnin."
  27,78,"Mass ik, s tidep, ad Iseyyi garasen s uĂȘuddu S. Neppa d Uzmir, d Amusnaw."
  27,79,"Ppkel $ef Ăebbi, ih, aql ak di tidep ipbegginen."
  27,80,"Ih, keĂ§Ă§, ur tepparav lmeggtin ad slen, ur tepparav iĂąeĂ©Ă©ugen ad slen i wancad, ma wexxĂŽen."
  27,81,"Ur fellak nnhaya ider$alen, mgal ttelfan nnsen. Ara islen, siwa wid iumnen s issekniyen nneÂŁ. Nitni d imvuĂąen."
  27,82,"Mi iĂ»aĂŽ wawal fellasen, ad asen d Nessuffe$ lweĂȘc si tmurt; ad asen yini ar imdanen ur metbutit $ef issekniyen nneÂŁ."
  27,83,"Ass ideg ara d Nefser, si yal lois, arbaĂą n wid inekĂŽen issekniyen nneÂŁ, d tirni,"
  27,84,"alamma, mi d usan, ad Yini: ""day tnekĂŽem issekniyen iW, ur ten teskecmem di tmusni? Ne$ d acu tellam txeddmem""?"
  27,85,"IĂ»aĂŽ wawal fellasen, imi densen. Ur d pmeslayen."
  27,86,"Day ur walan ara ar Nerra yasen iv i ureyyeĂȘ nnsen, ass iwakken ad walin? Deg wayagi, s tidep, issekniyen i ugdud iumnen."
  27,87,"Ass uĂ»uvu n lbuq, ad iagwad i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt, siwa wid i S ihwan i Ăebbi. A d asen akw $uĂŽeS, s uĂȘiwet."
  27,88,"A pwaliv idurar i t$ilev sebken, la teddun am usigna. D igi n Ăebbi i IĂ»egmen yal cci. Neppa, s tidep, IĂ©ĂŽa d acu txedmem."
  27,89,"Win id iusan s ise$, ad iawi it yifen. Widak, assen, mevmunit si tugdi."
  27,90,"Wid id iusan s tucmip, ad ppin wudmawen nnsen ar tmes. Ni$ a ppeppuqeĂźĂźim kan $ef wayen txeddmem?"
  27,91,"PwamĂŽe$ kan ad Ăąabde$ Mass n temdint agi, i IĂŽqa. IneS yal cci. PwamĂŽe$ d ad ili$ seg imduĂąen,"
  27,92,"ad male$ LeqwĂŽan. Win ipwanhan, ipwanha kan i iman is. Win innetlafen, ini: ""nek d aneddaĂŽ kan""."
  27,93,"Ini: ""a neckeĂŽ Ăebbi. Ad awen Issken issekniyen iS. A ten tĂąaqlem"". Mass ik ur I$effel ara $ef wayen txeddmem."
